---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for Chirag Singhal's Digital Identity">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--content-max-width)] px-6 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 text-xs text-teal-300/80 mb-6">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal-400 animate-pulse"></span>
        Legal
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/40 max-w-2xl">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="space-y-10 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not use our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">2. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise stated, we or our licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on this website. All intellectual property rights are reserved.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">3. User Obligations</h2>
        <p>You agree not to use the website in a way that may cause damage to the website or impairment of the availability or accessibility of the website; or in any way which is unlawful, illegal, fraudulent, or harmful. Code provided by the AI agent should be verified before use in production.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>We will not be held responsible or liable for any content, bugs, or errors arising from your use of the website or the generated AI content.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">5. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For any legal or Terms of Service related inquiries, please contact: <a href="mailto:hi@chirag127.in" class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 hover:underline ml-1 transition-colors">hi@chirag127.in</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
